(551, 77, 'about_content', '<div class="col-xs-24 content-info">\r\n<p class="text">With a combined 55+ years of third party administrative capabilities and medical stop loss experience, our team can tailor a self-insured benefits plan for any group of 50 lives or more nationwide.</p>\r\n<p class="text">Our expertise comes backed by thoroughly vetted self-insurance partners, including, but not limited to industry-leading health networks, claims management and adjudication, ERISA plan document creation, and medical stop-loss underwriters and carriers. Medical stop-loss insurance is an important component of a comprehensive health plan. We work closely with plan sponsors to keep costs under control and all interests aligned.</p>\r\n<p class="text"><span class="title">Real-time Resources</span> When we built Cook Group Solutions, one of our primary goals was to address the informational needs of the self-insurance ecosystem. Today, our Self-Insurance Knowledge Center gives brokers, agents, TPAs, benefits consultants and plan sponsors unprecedented access. This thoughtfully curated library of recent news, reports and white papers are just another tool in our arsenal dedicated to helping you navigate and thrive in the ever-changing self-insurance marketplace.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>'),
(552, 77, '_about_content', 'field_54d916fe0214d'),
(553, 74, 'about_title', 'Nationwide Coverage and Relationships.'),
(554, 74, '_about_title', 'field_54d916c30f7af'),
(555, 74, 'about_content', '<div class="col-xs-24 content-info">\r\n<p class="subtitle-blue">Currently administering <strong>75,000 self-insured covered lives</strong> across medical, pharmacy, dental and vision benefits. The Cook Group team has the third party administrative capabilities and medical stop loss experience to tailor a self-insured benefits plan for any group of 50 lives or more nationwide.</p>\r\nOur expertise comes backed by thoroughly vetted self-insurance partners, including, but not limited to industry-leading health networks, claims management and adjudication, ERISA plan document creation, and medical stop-loss underwriters and carriers. Medical stop-loss insurance is an important component of a comprehensive health plan. We work closely with plan sponsors to keep costs under control and all interests aligned.\r\n\r\n<strong>Real-time Resources.</strong>\r\n\r\nWhen we built Cook Group Solutions, one of our primary goals was to address the informational needs of the self-insurance ecosystem. Today, our Self-Insurance Knowledge Center gives brokers, agents, TPAs, benefits consultants and plan sponsors unprecedented access. This thoughtfully curated library of recent news, reports and white papers are just another tool in our arsenal dedicated to helping you navigate and thrive in the ever-changing self-insurance marketplace.\r\n\r\n</div>'),
