(2542, 267, 'producers_content', '<div class="col-xs-24 content-info">\r\n<p class="text">At Cook Group Solutions, we work with private sector employers, plan sponsors, independent agents and brokers, benefits consultants and self-insurance service providers to provide fair, competitive premiums backed by A-rated issuing insurance carriers and re-insurers. We specialize in working with employers transitioning from fully insured health benefits to self-insurance. More than protection, we pride ourselves in offering the flexibility, knowledge and resources our partners need to solve today’s unique healthcare challenges.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h3>Specialists in transitioning employers from fully insured to self-insured health benefit plans</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;">Health statements may not be required (case dependent)</blockquote>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h3>"A"-rated issuing carriers</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h3>Competitive commissions</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h3>Multiple underwriting markets</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>'),
(2543, 267, '_producers_content', 'field_54d8f918e82e4'),
(2544, 267, 'prod_content_', '<p class="text">We partner with creative carriers who are thorough in reviewing cases, and timely in processing claims payments. Our relationships include a broad selection of self-insurance vendors based on demographics, nationwide reach, and specialty. What does this mean for our partners? Access to more aggressive premium quotes than many of our competitors can offer. Registered nurse practitioners work alongside cost-containment vendors to make sure our clients pay reasonable fees for reliable services. Cook Group Solutions is recognized for enabling insured employees to get the best possible outcome without excessive burdens on an employer’s bottom-line.</p>'),
