(4947, 648, 'Home Main Content', '<span style="color: #266473;"><strong>Kathleen Gettelfinger, LMFT</strong></span>, As a Licensed Marriage and Family Therapist, I know firsthand the power of a safe and secure space that allows for exploration and examination. Seeking therapy is an act of both courage and vulnerability, and I meet these strengths with compassion, warmth, and understanding. Together, I work with clients to co-create an experience that facilitates honest reflection and a movement toward the change they seek. It is my privilege to accompany and support clients on this powerful journey of self-discovery.'),
(4946, 648, '_home_list_title', 'field_54d4dffe77262'),
